\id 1TH 531THKENU.SFM Kenyang New Testament June 2009
\h 1 Tɛsalónika
\toc1 Ɛkáti Pɔ̌l ɛnɛ́ mbɨ ntá Nkwɔ Tɛsalónika
\toc2 1 Nkwɔ Tɛsalónika
\toc3 1 Tɛs
\mt2 Ɛkáti Pɔ̌l ɛnɛ́ mbɨ ntá
\mt1 Nkwɔ Tɛsalónika
\c 1
\nb 
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔ̌l kɛ̌ nchí sɨ́ŋ ɛkáti ɛnɛ ntá yɛka nkwɔ Yesu abhɛn Tɛsalónika. Nchí sɨŋ ntá yɛka bǒ Mandɛm mmu achi Ɛtayɛsɛ nɛ be bho bǎbhárɛ́ mmʉɛt nɛ Yesu Kristo Acha. Nchí fá nɛ Sáilas nɛ Tímɔti. Mandɛm antɔ́ŋ be bɛrɨ̌ndu, anchyɛ bhe kpák.
\s1 Nɛka ɛnɛ́n bo Tɛsalónika
\p 
\v 2 Sɛ́chyɛ̀ bakak ntá Mandɛm mpoknkɛm ɛ̌ti yɛka mankɛm nɛ sɛ́fyɛ̀ bhé ndǔ nɛnɨkɨ́mʉɛt ɛnɛsɛ́ mpoknkɛm.
\v 3 Ɛ́chí ɛnyu ɛyɔ mbɔnyunɛ bɛsí Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ, sɛ́pú ghɔkɔntɨk bɛtɨk ɛbhɛn bǎkʉ̀ ndǔ bǎbhɔŋɔ nɛka nɛ Yesu, nɛ ɛnyǔ bǎdɛ́nɛ́ mmʉɛt ndǔ bɛtɨk ɛbhɛka ɛ̌ti ɛkɔŋ, nɛ ɛnyǔ bǎte kpirí ndǔ nɛbhakántɨ́ ɛnɛka nɛ Yesu Kristo Acha.
\v 4 Bɔ̌ma, sɛ́rɨ́ŋɨ́ bɛ́ Mandɛm akɔŋ be nɛ ayap be
\v 5 tɛ̌ndu Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ sɛ́ghàti bho abhɨkɨ twɔ nyaka ntá yɛka chí ndǔ ɛyɔŋɔ́nyu yɔyɔ, kɛ ndǔ bɛtaŋ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ nkwɔ. Nɛ bǎrɨŋɨ nyaka bɛ yɔ achi tɛtɛp. Mpok sɛ́chí awu nɛ bhe, bǎrɨŋɨ nyaka ɛnyǔ ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛyɛsɛ ɛchi. Sɛ́bhʉ̀rɛ nyaka mmʉɛt ɛyɛsɛ ɛnyu ɛyɔ ndu bɛkwak bhe!
\v 6 Nɛ bǎkóŋo ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛyɛsɛ nɛ ɛkakánɛkɔ Yesu Kristo Acha. Yɛ̌ndu bǎghɔ̀ nyaka bɛyǎ ɛsɔŋɔri, bǎsíɛ́pti Ɛyɔŋ Mandɛm nɛ maŋák amɛn Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ áchyɛ̀.
\v 7 Ɛ́kʉ bǎrɔ́p ɛrɨŋ ɛnɛ́ bakoŋo Yesu mankɛm atú Masidónia nɛ Akáiya máŋɔ̀kɔ.
\v 8 Nɛ Ɛyɔŋ Mandɛm ɛ́tàka atú Masidónia nɛ atú Akáiya ɛ̌ti mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bǎkʉ́, kɛ ɛ́bhɨ́kɨ́ may nɔ. Mbok nɛka ɛnɛka nɛ Mandɛm akɔ mbankɛm, ɛnyu ɛnɛ sɛbhɨkɨ bhɔŋ yɛ̌nyɨŋ bɛrɛm ndu bɛtɔŋ ɛnyǔ mǎnoko.
\v 9 Bɔ́ babhɔŋ bárɛ̀m ɛnyǔ básɔ́rɛ́ bhɛsɛ mpok sɛ́twɔ́ awu ntá yɛka nɛ ɛnyǔ bǎtɨknsɛm ntá bɔmandɛm nsé bǎrɔ́bhɛ chyɛ kɛnókó chi ntá Mandɛm. Yi aywǐnti kɛ achi Mandɛm anɛ tɛtɛp nɛ yi kɛ áchyɛ̀ nɛpɛ́m.
\v 10 Bǒ bhɔ bárɨ́ŋɨ́ nkwɔ bɛ mǎnòŋ Mmɔ Mandɛm ámfú amfay antwɔ. Nɔ chi, Yesu mmu Mandɛm ákʉ́ nyaka áfú ndǔ nɛwú apɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m. Yí wu kɛ ápɛ̀mɛ bhɛsɛ mpok Mandɛm átàŋ bo ndu ábè ntɨ nɛ bhɔ ɛ̌ti bɛbʉ́ bhap.
\c 2
\s1 Bɛtɨkɨ́ Pɔ̌l ákʉ́ ɛtɔk Tɛsalónika
\p 
\v 1 Bɔ̌ma, bǎbhɔŋ bɛrɨŋɨ bɛ nɛtwɔ́ anɛ sɛ́twɔ́ awu bɛghɔ bhe ápú nyaka ndɛ́ndɛm.
\v 2 Yɛ̌ndu mánáŋ báchyɛ́ nyaka bhɛsɛ bɛyǎ ɛsɔŋɔri nɛ ntíánwɔ́p ɛtɔk Fílipi mbɔ ɛnyu bǎrɨŋɨ, Mandɛm ywɛsɛ afyɛ́ bhɛsɛ ntɨ bɛ sɛ́ntwɔ́ sɛ́ngátí bhe Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ áfú ntá yi yɛ̌ndu bɛyǎ bo mánù nyaka tontó bɛchyɛt bhɛsɛ mbi.
\v 3 Bǎkɛ́ ghɔkɔntɨk bɛ́ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ́ sɛ́gháti bhe ɛ́chí tɛtɛp nɛ yɛ̌ bɛkwɛ́nɛ́ bɛpu arɛ́. Sɛ́bhɨ́kɨ́ bhɔ́ŋ nkaysi bɛ́rwɔ́ yɛ̌ mmu.
\v 4 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ sɛ́kʉ̀ chi bɛ, tɛ̌ndu Mandɛm áyɨ́ŋɨ́ ághɔ́ bɛ sɛ́kwǎy bo abhɛn yi afyɛ́ Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ amɔ́, nɔ kɛ sɛ́ghàti bho yɔ. Nɛ puyɛ̌ chi bɛ bo mámbɔ́ŋ maŋák nɛ bhɛsɛ, kɛ chí bɛ́ Mandɛm mmu áyɨ̀ŋɨ bɛghɔ ɛnyǔ bati ayɛsɛ achi amɛm, ámbɔ́ŋ maŋák nɛ bhɛsɛ.
\v 5 Bǎrɨŋɨ nkwɔ bɛ mpok sɛ́chí nɛ bhe sɛ́bhɨ́kɨ́ sɔt sɛ́rwɔrɛ́nyu bɛkʉ mǎmbɔ́ŋ maŋák. Nɛ mbɔŋ Mandɛm achi ntísiɛ bɛ sɛ́pú ghati nyaka bhe Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ chí nɛ nkaysi bɛbhɔŋ nsáy anɛ áfù ntá yɛka.
\v 6 Nɛ sɛ́pú kʉ nyaka yɛ̌nyɨŋ bɛ́ yɛ̌ chi be, yɛ chi bo báchak, mánkaka bhɛsɛ. Sɛ́kwáy nyaka bɛbhɛp be mɛnyɨŋ mbɔ bǒnto Kristo.
\v 7 Kɛ sɛ́kɔ́pti bhe mbɔ ɛnyǔ nnɔ ákɛ̀m bɔ̌bhi.
\v 8 Sɛ́kɔŋ be tontó, kpát ɛ́kʉ́ sɛ́ká bɛ sɛbhɔŋ bɛchyɛ be, puyɛ̌ chí ndiɛrɛ Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ áfú ntá Mandɛm, kɛ yɛ chi mmʉɛt ɛyɛsɛ nkwɔ ndǔ bǎchí bhɛsɛ antɨ tontó.
\v 9 Bɔ̌ma, bǎbhɨ́kɨ́ ghɔkɔntɨk ndu sɛ́re kʉ bɛtɨk, sɛ́mkpɔt nɔkɔ nsɔ́ŋti bɛti nɛ ngósí mpok sɛ́chí awu nɛ bhe. Sɛ́kʉ̀ nyaka bɛtɨk ɛnyu yɔ bɛ sɛ́mbɔ́ŋ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́chɛ́bhɛ́ bhɛsɛ. Sɛ́bhɨ́kɨ́ yaŋ nyaka bɛbhak ntu ntá yɛka mpok sɛ́ghàti bhe Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ áfú ntá Mandɛm.
\v 10 Bǎchi batísiɛ bhɛsɛ. Mandɛm nkwɔ achi ntísiɛ bɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛsɛ́ nɛntɨ ɛnɛka bakoŋo Yesu nɛchí nyáká nyáŋá nɛ chak nɛ nɛ́kɛ bhɔŋ bɛkwɛ́nɛ́ bɛsí Mandɛm.
\v 11 Bǎrɨŋɨ ɛnyu sɛ́kɛ̀m nyaka yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka mbɔ ɛnyǔ chi bhɔ ákɛ̀m bɔ̌bhi.
\v 12 Sɛ́fyɛ̀ nyaka bhe ntɨ nɛ sɛ́kpɛ̀mɛ nyaka bhe bɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛka nɛ́nchyɛ Mandɛm maŋák. Yí kɛ ábhɨ́ŋɨ́ bhe bɛ mǎmbak bo abhɛn yi achi Mfɔ wap nɛ bɛ mǎmbák ndu kɛnɛ́m ɛki nɛ yi.
\p 
\v 13 Nɛ nkwɔ sɛ́kàka Mandɛm mpoknkɛm mbɔnyunɛ mpok sɛ́gháti bhe Ɛyɔŋ ɛyi, bǎbhɨ́kɨ́ sɔt yɔ́ mbɔ ɛyɔŋ ɛnɛ nkwǎ. Bǎsɔ́t bɛ tɛtɛp chi Ɛyɔŋ Mandɛm ɛnɛ́ ɛ́kʉ̀ bɛtɨk amɛm batɨ yɛka, be bho mánóko.
\v 14 Bɔ̌ma, bǎrɔp bo abhɛn mǎŋɔkɔ ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛnɛ́ bǒnkwɔ Mandɛm abhɛn atú Judɛ́ya. Bǎbhárɛ́ mmʉɛt nɛ Yesu Kristo mbɔnyunɛ bǎghɔ̌ ɛsɔŋɔri amɔ batɨ bo ɛtɔk ɛyɛka nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ bo Israɛl báchyɛ́ nyaka bhɔ ɛsɔŋɔri atú Judɛ́ya.
\v 15 Bo Israɛl bhɔ kɛ báwáy nyaka Yesu Acha nɛ barɛmɛ́ kɛpɨ̌ntɨ Mandɛm nɛ bɔ́ kɛ báboko bhɛsɛ ɛtɔk. Bákʉ̀ ntɨ nɛ́mbé Mandɛm. Bachi bǒmpap ntá yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu.
\v 16 Bo Israɛl bhɔ báchɛ̀t bhɛsɛ mbi bɛ sɛkɛ ghati bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ Mandɛm ámpɛ́mɛ́ bhɔ. Bákʉ́ bɛbʉ́ kpát mánáŋá. Kɛ bákʉ́ kpát bɛběntɨ Mandɛm bɛchi nɛ bhɔ.
\s1 Pɔ̌l abhɔŋ ntɨ bɛrɔŋ Tɛsalónika
\p 
\v 17 Bɔ̌ma, yɛ̌ndu bákʉ́ sɛ́rɔ́ nyaka bhe ndu mɔ́mbɨŋɨ́ mpok, batɨ yɛsɛ ábhʉ́ɛ́t nyaka nɛ bhe, nɛ ɛ́kʉ́ ɛkwak bɛpɛt bɛghɔ bhe bɛsí nɛ bɛsi ɛ́re yá ɛ́ndɔk nɔkɔ chi ambɨ nɛ sɛre nu bɛghɔ bhe.
\v 18 Sɛ́yàŋ nyaka bɛ́twɔ awu ntá yɛka. Mɛmbɔŋ Pɔ̌l, mmɔ́ bɛ́twɔ awu ndɔŋ nɛ ndɔŋ, kɛ Satan achɛ́t bhɛsɛ mbi.
\v 19 Pú sɛ́bháká ntɨ chi nɛ bhe? Pú be kɛ̌ báchyɛ̀ bhɛsɛ maŋák-á? Pú be kɛ̌ bǎkʉ̀ sɛ́ndɛp chɔŋ awɔ́ antɨ bɛsí Yesu Acha ywɛsɛ ndǔ nywɔp ɛnɛn yi apɛtnsɛm, bɛ sɛ́kʉ bɛtɨk ɛbhɛsɛ́ sayri?
\v 20 Tɛtɛp, be kɛ bǎkʉ sɛ́dɛ̀p awɔ́ antɨ, nɛ be kɛ báchyɛ̀ bhɛsɛ bɛyǎ maŋák.
\c 3
\nb 
\v 1 Sɛ́chɔ́kɔ́ kpát, sɛ́kɛ pɛrɛ kwáy bɛkɛpntɨ, sɛ́ka bɛrɔp ansɛm ndu ɛtɔk Atɛns,
\v 2 sɛ́tó mɔ́mayɛsɛ Tímɔti ntá yɛká. Yí achí ntɨ nkʉbɛtɨk Mandɛm ndu bɛ́gháti bho Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ ɛ̌ti Kristo. Sɛ́tó yi bɛ ámfyɛ bhe ntɨ, ankʉ mǎnté kpirí ndǔ nɛka ɛnɛka,
\v 3 bɛ yɛ̌ mmu ywɛka amɔt ákɛ́ kwɛn ansɛm ɛ̌ti bɛsɔŋɔri ɛbhɛn. Bě babhɔŋ bǎrɨŋɨ bɛ, bɛkoŋo nkaysi Mandɛm, bɛsɔŋɔri ɛbhɛn bɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛ́tɛ́mɛ́ri bhɛsɛ.
\v 4 Mpok sɛ́chí nyaka nɛ bhe, sɛ́ghàti nyaka be ambɨ ambɨ bɛ chɔŋ sɛ́mbɔŋ bɛsɔŋɔri, nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ ɛ́fákárí, nɛ bǎrɨŋɨ ɛnyu ɛyɔ.
\v 5 Ɛ̌ti yɔ, mpok mbɨ́kɨ́ pɛrɛ kway bɛ́kɛpntɨ, ntó Tímɔti bɛ ántwɔ́, ángɔ́ mbák babhʉɛ́t bɛ́sɨ́kɨ ntɨ nɛ Kristo. Mbɔ̌ŋ nyaka bɛcháy bɛ ngufú Satan mmu ámɔ̀ bo ndu bɛkʉ bɔ bákɛ́pɛrɛ noko Yesu, abhɔŋ mbi nɛ bhe nɛ bɛtɨk ɛbhɛsɛ mɛnkɛm bɛrɔŋ ndɛ́ndɛm.
\p 
\v 6 Kɛ Tímɔti anáŋ áfǔ awu apɛtnsɛm fá, nɛ ɛrɨ́tí ntó bɛ bǎtaŋ ndǔ nɛsɨkɨ́ntɨ ɛnɛka nɛ Kristo nɛ ndǔ ɛkɔŋ ɛnɛ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ nɛ batɨ. Nɛ aghátí bhɛsɛ bɛ bǎkàysi bhɛsɛ nɛ maŋák mpoknkɛm nɛ bǎbhɔŋ ɛkwak bɛghɔ bhɛsɛ nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ sɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ ɛkwak bɛghɔ bhe.
\v 7 Bɔ̌ma, ɛkʉ yɛ bɛ yɛ̌ndu báchyɛ̀ bhɛsɛ́ nɛnyok nɛ bɛyǎ ɛsɔŋɔri, batɨ apɔp bhɛsɛ amɛm mbɔnyunɛ bǎte kpirí ndu nɛsɨkɨ́ntɨ ɛnɛka nɛ Kristo.
\v 8 Tɛ̌ndu bǎte kpirí ndu mbi Yesu Acha, sɛ́chí sayri.
\v 9 Ntɨkɨ ɛnyu bakak sɛ́kway bɛchyɛ Mandɛm ɛ̌ti maŋák mankɛm amɛn sɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛsí bhi ɛ̌ti yɛka?
\v 10 Sɛ́nɨ̀kmʉɛt nɛ batɨ yɛsɛ ankɛm bɛti nɛ ngósí bɛ́ Mandɛm ánkwak sɛmpɛt sɛngɔ bhe bɛsí nɛ bɛsi, nɛ sɛ́ntɔŋ be mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bǎbhɨ́kɨ́re rɨŋɨ, ndu bɛkwak mǎmbɔŋ nɛka nɛ Kristo mbɔ ɛnyǔ ɛ́yaŋ.
\p 
\v 11 Sɛ́nɨkmʉɛt bɛ Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ yímbɔŋ nɛ Yesu Kristo Acha mánkʉ sɛ́ntwɔ ntá yɛka.
\v 12 Sɛ́nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ Yesu Acha ánkʉ ɛkɔŋ ɛyɛka nɛ batɨ nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu achak ɛ́ngó ɛ́ndɔ́k nɔ́kɔ́ chí ambɨ, nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛkɔŋ ɛnɛ sɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ ntá yɛka.
\v 13 Sɛ́nɨ̀kmʉɛt ɛnyu ɛyɔ bɛ yi ankʉ batɨ ántáŋ be amɛm nɛ bɛ́ bǎkɛ́ bhɔŋ bɛkwɛ́nɛ́, nɛ bɛ́ mǎmbák nyáŋá bɛsí Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ, kɛ mpok anɛ Yesu Kristo Acha átwɔ̀ nɛ bo Mandɛm ankway.
\c 4
\s1 Nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛn Mandɛm akɔŋɔ
\p 
\v 1 Bɔ̌ma, ndu bɛrɔŋ ambɨ, sɛ́ghati bhe ɛnyǔ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛbhʉrɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛka nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ bǎkʉ̀ nɔ bɛ Mandɛm ámbɔ́ŋ maŋák nɛ bhe. Sɛ́nɨ̀k yɛ be mmʉɛt sɛ́mkpɛmɛ nɔkɔ ndu nnyɛ́n Yesu Acha bɛ mǎndɔk ambɨ bɛkʉ nɔ.
\v 2 Bě babhɔŋ bǎrɨŋɨ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn sɛ́ghátí nyaka bhe ndǔ nnyɛ́n Yesu Acha bɛ bǎbhɔŋ bɛ́kʉ.
\v 3 Ɛnyɨŋ Mandɛm áyàŋ chi bɛ mǎmbák nyáŋá, bɛ bǎkɛ́ bhɔŋ yɛ̌nyɨŋ bɛkʉ nɛ barak ɛ́pusi.
\v 4 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ankɛ́m mmʉɛt ɛyi, \f + \fr 4:4 \ft “Bɛkɛm mmʉɛt:” Ɛ́kway nkwɔ bɛbhak bɛ, “Ándɨ́ŋɨ́ ndu áchɔkɔ nɛ ngɔrɛ́ ywi”.\f* ɛnyu ɛnɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛni nɛ́bhak pɛ́pɛ́p bɛsí Mandɛm, nɛ bo mámbɔŋ kɛnókó nɛ yi.
\v 5 Bǎkɛ́ ŋwaka ndǔ barak ɛ́pusi, kɛkɛ́m mmʉɛt mbɔ bo abhɛn babhɨ́kɨ́ rɨŋɨ Mandɛm.
\v 6 Yɛ̌ mmú ákɛ́ kʉ ntɨ bɛbʉ́ ndǔ ndaká kɛbhʉrɛ anɛ́, nɛ yɛ̌ mmu ákɛ́ nyiɛ ntɨ ɛ́bhɔ́ŋ! Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ Yesu Acha ǎkɛmɛ kɛ́mbé ntá bo abhɛn bákʉ̀ mɛnyǔ bɛbʉ́ ɛbhɔ mɛnkɛm nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ sɛ́náŋ sɛ́gháti bhe bɛ mǎnsɔt mpok.
\v 7 Mandɛm abhɨ́kɨ́ bhɨŋɨ bhɛsɛ chí bɛ sɛmbak bǒ ɛpúsí, abhɨ́ŋɨ́ bhɛsɛ bɛ sɛ́mbak nyáŋá bɛsí bhi.
\v 8 Yɛ̌ agha anɛ ábyàk yɛ ndak anɛ apú byak chi nkwǎ, ǎbyàk chí Mandɛm mmu áchyɛ̀ bhe Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ yi.
\p 
\v 9 Nti apú bɛsɨŋ be bɛ mǎmbɔ́ŋ ɛkɔŋ nɛ batɨ̌ bakoŋo Yesu. Mandɛm yímbɔŋ anáŋ átɔ́ŋ be ɛnyu bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛkɔŋ batɨ.
\v 10 Nɛ tɛtɛp, bǎkɔŋ batɨ̌ bǒnkwɔ atú Masidónia ankɛm. Kɛ bɔmá, sɛ́ghàti bhe bɛ́ ɛkɔŋ ɛnɛ́ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ nɛ batɨ ɛ́ndɔ́k nɔ́kɔ́ chi ambɨ.
\v 11 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ánkʉ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ bɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛni nɛ́kɛ́ chyɛ bho ɛsɔŋɔri. Mmu ákɛ́ chwe ndǔ ndaká ntɨ. Nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka abhɔŋ bɛkʉ bɛtɨk nɛ amɔ́ yi nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ sɛ́ghátí nyaka bhe.
\v 12 Mǎmbák ɛnyu ɛyɔ bɛ́ bo abhɛn bábhɨ́kɨ́ noko mánchyɛ́ bhe kɛnókó nɛ bɛ́ bǎkɛ́ kɔ bɛsɨ́kɨ́.
\s1 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ ɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛfakari nɛ báwú kɛ Yesu Acha antwɔ́
\p 
\v 13 Bɔ̌ma, nɛ́nɛ, sɛ́yàŋ bɛkʉ bɛ bǎkɛ́ rɔp amɛm ɛjuri bɛ́yɨ́ŋɨ bo abhɛn bágú bɛ bǎkɛ́ di bhɔ mbɔ bo abhɛn bábhɨ́kɨ́ bhakantɨ bɛ chɔŋ bawú mámpɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m.
\v 14 Tɛ̌ndu sɛ́nókó bɛ́ Yesu ágú nyaka, apɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m, sɛ́noko nkwɔ bɛ chɔŋ Mandɛm ankʉ bakoŋo Yesu abhɛn bágú mámpɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m mpok Yesu átwɔ.
\v 15 Bɛ́kóŋo ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ mbɔŋ Yesu Acha árɛ́mɛ́, sɛ́ghàti bhe bɛ mpok Yesu Acha átwɔ́, bɛsɛ́ bho sɛchi nɛpɛ́m sɛ́pú yambɨ bɛ́tɛ́mɛri yi kɛ abhɛn bágú mántɛmɛri yi.
\v 16 Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ chɔŋ mbɔŋ Yesu Acha amfú amfay antwɔ́ anchyɛ ɛyɔŋ nɛ bɛtaŋ. Mfɔ bɔángɛl Mandɛm andɛm nɛ ɛyɔŋ ɛtaŋataŋ, nɛ mmbá Mandɛm ankwɛ́n. Ɛ́mfakari yɛ bɛ́ bakoŋó Kristo abhɛn bágú mánjambɨ mámpɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m,
\v 17 kɛ bɛsɛ́ bho sɛchi nɛpɛ́m nɛ sɛ́bhʉɛ́t ansɛm, sɛ́nko ndǔ nɛbháŋ tɛ́mté nɛ bhɔ, sɛ́ntɛmɛri Yesu Acha ndǔ yi ásɛ̀p. Nɛ bɛbho mpok ɛyɔ, sɛ́mbak nɛ yi mpoknkɛm.
\v 18 Chiɛ́ nɔ́kɔ́ yɛka batɨ nɛpɔptǐntɨ́ nɛ bɛyɔŋ ɛbhɛn.
\c 5
\s1 Bák ká pě ndu mɛnoŋ Yesu Acha
\p 
\v 1 Bɔ̌ma, ntí apú bɛsɨŋ be ɛ̌ti mbɔ̌ŋ mpok anɛ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛ́fákari.
\v 2 Bǎbhɔŋ bɛ́rɨŋɨ bɛ nywɔp Yesu Acha átwɔ̀ nɛ́bhak chɔŋ mbɔ ngɛ́p anɛ átwɔ̀ nɛ bɛti.
\v 3 Mpok anɛ bo bárɛ̀m bɛ, “Mbǎŋ achi kpák, yɛ ɛsɔŋɔri ɛ́pu.” Mpok ɛyɔ kɛ̌ ɛrɛ̌m ɛsɔŋɔri ɛ́kwɛn bɔ amʉɛt tɛ́mchok mbɔ bɛbe ngɔrɛ́ anɛ ánòŋsi. Nɛ mbi bɛ́bʉ́ɛ kɛbhák.
\p 
\v 4 Bɔ̌ma, kɛ mbák chí bhe, bǎpú amɛm ɛjuri, bɛ́ nywɔp ɛnɔ nɛ́mfɔ́kɔ́rí bhe mbɔ ngɛ́p.
\v 5 Bǎchí bo abhɛn bǎkɔ̀ nɛ ngósí, mpok mbaŋ ághɔ̀. Sɛ́pú bo ɛjuri, sɛ́pú bo bɛti.
\v 6 Sɛ́kɛ́ bhʉrɛ yɛ kɛnɔ́ mbɔ mbɔk bho. Sɛ́mbák chí pě, sɛ́nkɛm nɔkɔ mmʉɛt.
\v 7 Bo abhɛn bábhʉ̀rɛ kɛnɔ́, bábhʉ̀rɛ chi nɛ bɛ́ti, nɛ bo bákwɛ̀n mmɛ́m chí nɛ bɛti.
\v 8 Kɛ tɛ̌ndu sɛ́chí chí bǒ ngósí, sɛ́nkɛ́m mmʉɛt. Sɛ́ndɔ́k ambɨ mɛ́nóko Yesu nɛ bɛ́bhɔŋ ɛkɔŋ nɛ bo, bɛ ɛyɔ ɛmbák mbɔ kɛndɛ́n anɛ ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu ákɛ́mɛ́ bɛchyɛt mmʉɛt. Sɛ́mbáká ntɨ bɛ chɔŋ Yesu ampɛmɛ bhɛsɛ, nɛ bɛ ɛyɔ ɛ́mbák ntá yɛsɛ́ mbɔ ntá ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu anɛ ákuti ntí ywi.
\v 9 Bǎrɨ́ŋɨ́ bɛ Mandɛm abhɨ́kɨ́ yap bhɛsɛ chi bɛ sɛ́mbák bo abhɛn yi átàŋ anchyɛ ntɛmsi. Ayap bhɛsɛ chi bɛ ánkʉ Yesu Kristo Acha ámpɛmɛ bhɛsɛ.
\v 10 Yesu ágú ɛ̌ti yɛsɛ́ bɛ yi ánáŋ ántwɔ́, yɛ̌ sɛbhʉɛt chí pě, yɛ̌ sɛ́gǔ gu, sɛ́nkwáy bɛ́bhak nɛ yi.
\v 11 Ndu ɛ́chí nɔ, fyɛ́ nɔ́kɔ́ yɛ́ka batɨ ntɨ mǎnkwak nɔkɔ batɨ nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ bǎkʉ̀ nɔ.
\s1 Bɛyɔŋɔ́ ngwɛnti
\p 
\v 12 Bɔ̌ma, sɛ́ghàti bhe bɛ mǎnchyɛ́ nɔkɔ bǒ abhɛn bákʉ̀ bɛtɨk Acha ndǔ nkwɔ ywɛka kɛnókó bɛ mánchyɛ nɔkɔ bhe maniɛ bɛ bǎkɛ́ kʉ bɛbʉ́.
\v 13 Bǎbhɔŋ bɛchyɛ bhɔ bɛyǎ kɛnókó, mǎnkɔŋ bɔ́ ɛ̌ti bɛtɨk ɛbhɛ́n bɔ bákʉ̀. Nɛ mǎmbák sayri nɛ batɨ.
\v 14 Bɔ̌ma, sɛmtí nɔ́kɔ́ bábhɔ́t, mǎmfyɛ nɔkɔ abhɛn bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛcháy ntɨ. Kwak nɔ́kɔ́ ká abhɛn mmʉɛt ápú bhɔ. Bɔ́ŋ ká ɛkɛ́bhɛ́ntɨ nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu.
\v 15 Ghɔ́ ká bɛ yɛ̌ mmu ákɛ́ kɛmɛ bɛbʉ́ amfǎy bɛbʉ́. Nu nɔ́kɔ́ ká bɛkʉ chi bɛrɨ̌ndu ntá batɨ bǒnkwɔ nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu achak.
\v 16 Bák ká maŋák mpoknkɛm,
\v 17 mǎnɨk nɔkɔ mmʉɛt mpoknkɛm.
\v 18 Nɛ yɛ̌ ɛ́mbak bɛ yi, chyɛ́ nɔ́kɔ́ ká Mandɛm bakak, tɛ̌ndu mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn mɛnkɛm chi ɛbhɛn yi áyàŋ mǎnkʉ́ ndǔ bǎchí bo Yesu Kristo.
\v 19 Bǎkɛ́ nɛmɛ ngó Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ.
\v 20 Bǎkɛ́ byák ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ ákʉ́ ntɨ mǔnkwɔ ándɛm.
\v 21 Bǎbhɔŋ bɛchak yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ sayri, mǎnkɛm ɛ́nɛ ɛ́rɨ́.
\v 22 Bǎkɛ́ bhɔŋ ɛnyɨŋ bɛkʉ nɛ barak abʉ́abʉ.
\p 
\v 23 Mbɔ̌ŋ Mandɛm mmu áchɨ̀ɛ kpák ánkʉ́ mǎmbák nyáŋá ndǔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mbi. Yímbɔŋ ámbʉ́rɛ́ nkaysi, nɛ ɛfóŋó, nɛ mmʉɛt yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ɛnyu ɛnɛ́ ápú bhɔŋ bɛkwɛ́nɛ́ kpátɛ mpok Yesu Kristo Acha átwɔ.
\v 24 Mandɛm mmu ábhɨ́ŋɨ́ be bɛ mǎmbák bǒbhi, ǎbhʉ̀rɛ bariɛp ami, nɛ chɔŋ ankʉ nɔ.
\v 25 Bɔ̌ma, fyɛ́ ká bhɛsɛ ndǔ nɛnɨkɨ́mʉɛt.
\v 26 Kaká ká batɨ nɛ ɛkɔŋ Mandɛm.
\v 27 Nchí ghati bhe ndǔ nnyɛ́n Yesu Acha bɛ mǎmpáy ɛkáti ɛnɛ ntá bǒnkwɔ mankɛm.
\v 28 Bɛrɨ̌ndu Yesu Kristo Acha mɛ́mbák nɛ bhe.
